Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Great football news and expert sports insight on underdog teams against the spread in college footbal and NFL pro football throughout the season. Other sports, such as basketball, baseball and hockey are covered in the football off-season too!

If you love football, this is the skill for you. We talk nfc, afc, ncaa, aac, acc, big ten, big 12, conference usa (c-usa), mac, mwc, pac-12, sec and sunbelt.

Sportscaster TJ Rives is the sideline reporter for the Buccaneers Radio Network. He is also the play-by-play announcer for Tampa Bay Rays homes games on the Compass Media Networks. He is a talk host for Fox Sports Radio as a host of Fox Sports Radio Saturday Night.
